==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Granitic
<hw>Gra*nit"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
granitique.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Like granite in composition, color,
etc.; having the nature of granite; <as>as, granitic
texture</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Consisting of granite; <as>as, <ex>granitic</ex>
mountains</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Granitical</ent>⟦br⟧
